# Bootstrap data for in-memory vector store
#
# This directory contains exported vector store data for bootstrapping
# the in-memory vector store in CLI and development environments.
#
# Files:
# - tables.json: Core system table metadata
# - tables_embeddings.npz: Precomputed embeddings for tables
# - nuance.json: SQL patterns and best practices
# - nuance_embeddings.npz: Precomputed embeddings for nuance
# - codebook.json: Field definitions and mappings
# - codebook_embeddings.npz: Precomputed embeddings for codebook
# - manifest.json: Export metadata and statistics
#
# To regenerate:
#   python scripts/export_vector_store_snapshot.py
